{"id":232677282,"title":"法國懸案《誰殺了小男孩？》","content":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOB.jpg\n\n如果你喜歡看真實案件紀錄節目，請別錯過這部《誰殺了小男孩？》（Grégory）。節目中描述的，是發生於 1984 年 10 月 16 日、法國小鎮的一起謀殺案，被害者是 4 歲男童 Grégory Villemin。本節目共五集，除了呈現相關的資料畫面，也訪談了幾位當初參與調查的人員、律師和記者。這起案件將整個 Villemin 家族都牽扯進來，甚至連 Grégory 的母親都一度被懷疑是兇手。當年的偵辦方式更是粗糙到不行，導致多年來雖有數名對象被懷疑，卻因缺乏直接證據而沒能找到真兇。最令人憤怒的是媒體的嗜血態度和公審式的報導，讓輿論像獵巫一般，對相關人士未審先判。事發至今已滿 35 年，究竟真相能否有水落石出的一天？\n\n預告\nhttps://youtu.be/H--DnsJ62Mw\n\n歡迎追蹤粉專\nhttps://www.facebook.com/TVnMovieWatchers/","excerpt":"如果你喜歡看真實案件紀錄節目，請別錯過這部《誰殺了小男孩？》（Grégory）。節目中描述的，是發生於 1984 年 10 月 16 日、法國小鎮的一起謀殺案，被害者是 4 歲男童 Grégory V","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"0a859162-88d8-4406-8111-71c57aae84a1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-13T03:14:53.585Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T03:14:53.585Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":44,"tags":[],"topics":["Netflix","法國","懸案","犯罪"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"Netflix","forumAlias":"netflix","school":"影劇業餘觀察團 - 老大","department":"kevin781109","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":43},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOB.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"775c81f8-ace7-4fbb-8e38-cc0b6bf73518","url":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOBl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOBl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOBl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-13T03:14:53.585Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-13T03:14:53.585Z"},{"id":"775c81f8-ace7-4fbb-8e38-cc0b6bf73518","url":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOB.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/aJbUvOB","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/aJbUvOBl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","